    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A circular letter received at the\nmayors office this morning gives\nthe details of a monster indigna-\nton meeting to be held on the\nSpokane street speaking situation\nnext Sunday night in San Francis\nco, at which such noted speakers\nas Jack London, the novelist, Ern-\nest Untermann, socialist writer;\nAustin Lewis, Charles Edward\nRussell and other literary lights\nwill be present. p Fl. Mccarthy,\nthe labor mayor-elect of San Fran\ncisco, has been asked to be\npresent."
    }
